Interface KWHashMap<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - is the type for the keys
    V - is the type for the values
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChainHashMap, ChainHashMap2, CoalescedHashMap

    public interface KWHashMap<K,V>
    An interface for classes that will act like an HashMap.
